OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FRescuers are racing against the clock
OL,7,Fto find survivors after a landslide in
OL,8,Fthe southwestern Chinese city of
OL,9,FChongqing killed at least eight people
OL,10,Fand left 34 missing.
OL,12,FIt occurred in Pengshui County on
OL,13,FFriday when massive amounts of rocks
OL,14,Fand soil washed down a slope, burying
OL,15,Fmore than 10 residential buildings.
OL,17,FState broadcaster CCTV said 10 people
OL,18,Fwere taken to hospital and more than
OL,19,F1,100 have been forced to evacuate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
