OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FOn Saturday, images and videos showed
OL,7,Fthat one of the fallen rocks appeared
OL,8,Flarger than a multi-storey block, with
OL,9,Fruins scattered across the steep
OL,10,Fterrain.
OL,12,FOne of the damaged buildings had its
OL,13,Ftop part crushed and a car was seen
OL,14,Fhalf-buried near another.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
