OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784429266
OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FThe landslide contained about 18,000
OL,7,Fcubic meters (635,500 cubic feet) of
OL,8,Frocks and debris, and the largest
OL,9,Fsingle rock was around 3,000 cubic
OL,10,Fmeters (106,000 cubic feet), Wang
OL,11,FChuanjun, head of Planning and Natural
OL,12,FResources in Pengshui County, told a
OL,13,Fnews conference.
OL,15,FLocal media said persistent rain hit
OL,16,FPengshui from Friday night to Saturday
OL,17,Fmorning, with 19.2 centimetres (nearly
OL,18,F8 inches) recorded at a weather
OL,19,Fstation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
