OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FThe unstable weather made the rescue
OL,7,Foperation more challenging, CCTV said.
OL,9,FAs the downpour eased slightly, crews
OL,10,Fentered the site to conduct on-the-
OL,11,Fground inspections of the collapsed
OL,12,Fbuildings and riverbank areas.
OL,14,FWhile rescue operations are being
OL,15,Fcarried out on one side of the massive
OL,16,Frocks, teams will later need to look
OL,17,Fbeneath them, where they may risk
OL,18,Finjury if the boulders become unstable
OL,19,Fand slide, CCTV reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
