OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FOnce the search of the surrounding
OL,7,Fareas is complete, officers will drill
OL,8,Finto the boulders and fill the holes
OL,9,Fwith explosives to break them apart,
OL,10,Fit said.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FBeyond the deployment of excavators, a
OL,18,FCCTV video report showed a search dog
OL,19,Fbarking to alert a rescuer about signs
OL,20,Fof life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
