OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FVolunteers rode on motorbikes to
OL,7,Fdeliver supplies to rescuers and some
OL,8,Fstranded residents. Other residents in
OL,9,FPengshui reported that the water
OL,10,Fsupply to their homes was only
OL,11,Favailable at certain intervals.
OL,13,FChina's National Development and
OL,14,FReform Commission on Saturday
OL,15,Fallocated a relief fund of 30 million
OL,16,Fyuan (#3.29 million) to support the
OL,17,Frestoration of infrastructure and
OL,18,Fpublic service facilities following
OL,19,Fthe disaster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
