OL,3,CRescuers race to find survivors after
OL,4,Clandslide kills at least eight in China
OL,6,FThe rain-triggered landslide occurred
OL,7,Fnear a stretch of the Wujiang River,
OL,8,Fwhich cuts through karst mountains
OL,9,Fpeppered with small towns and terraces.
OL,11,FPengshui County is located in the
OL,12,Fsoutheast part of Chongqing, bordering
OL,13,Fthe provinces of Hubei and Guizhou.
